author: Alois
title: Main Page
text:
Private data : (3030) only accessible to staff members Recent new additions 
Please click on the link 'New Pages' in the navigation box on the left, or look in the right column near the bottom for the list 'New in Astrodatabank'. 
Updates appear regularily, nearly every day. Submitting new data or corrections 
For submitting new data from qualified sources, please send either email to adbdata@astro.com or use the Astrodienst Forum thread New candidates for Astro-Databank . 
For submitting corrections to existing entries, please use the same email address or the Forum thread Corrections of existing Astro-Databank entries . Other information Information for owners of Astrodatabank 3.0 and Astrodatabank 4.0 software Forum: There is a special Astrodienst forum area for discussion of charts. The 'newsmaker' discussion of the previous astrodatabank.com website has been transfered there, and contains 34'000 user postings. History: For the more recent history, please see the project description page , for the earlier history please see The Rodden-ISAR Databank . Copyright: Please see the copyright page for information about the user rights regarding this wiki and the data in it. Registration: This is a currently a read-only wiki. Registration as a user is not required, see also Astro-Databank:Registration Bad astrology: See the page Bad astrology . Not everyone offering astrology is honest or benevolent.
